====================================================
GOALS
====================================================

Create one of the most complete Paper plugins for SMP servers.

The plugin must be:

• Extremely optimized
• Thread-safe
• Expandable
• Well documented
• Easy to maintain
• Compatible with popular Paper plugins
• Safe for production servers
• Minimal TPS impact

